job
usage to run a job based on script when required
create yaml file and apply
kubectl get jobs and get pods
kubectl logs pod name to get o/p
create cron job and apply
kubectl get cronjobs

kubectl logs helloworld-pvkcm
kubectl describe helloworld-pvkcm


helm create chart name
default structre will be created.. we can modify and call as variables with value as main file
helm lint path - to check the error
helm template - to check variables are replaced with values
helm package name
helm repo list
curl --data-binary "@repotest-0.1.0.tgz" http://192.168.1.50:8080/api/charts adding to ip address where we have installed chartmusem
helm search repo mychartmuseumrepo to check the packages added in repo
helm repo update to update the reposity with the charts
helm plugin list
helm push chartname - to push directly in repo without creating zip file
once pushed update repo using helm repo update and check for the repositries using helm search repo repositry name


rollback steps
go to directory and show the yaml files
helm create chart name
helm install release name and chart name
helm history release name
helm get all release name
helm rollback release name revision number


cron
create job and cron yaml files
kubectl get jobs
kubectl logs and podname
kubectl get cronjobs

helm charts
explain chart,values, deployment and service files
helm repo list
helm search repo mychartmuseumrepo
if charts added it will be listed if not we can add it by using helm repo add name and url
helm repo update
helm install mychartmuseumrepo/repotest --generate-name
helm ls
helm create chartname
once we create default files will be added
helm package chartname
make changes and package it using helm package chart name so that it creates tz file	
helm push chartname/repo name
curl --data-binary "package name" url (repo url)
helm repo update
helm install repo/chartnames --generate-name

make changes for replicas in values and update version
helm upgrade release name and chart name
kubectl get all
helm history release name
helm rollback release name


